dct_description_sm: "Plan expédié établi en 1950 au moyen de photographies aériennes redressées et assemblées à l'aide des documents cadastraux existants." "Direction des travaux publics." Map comprises three separate sheets joined to form one. Map shows administrative boundaries. Legend is hand drawn and colored denoting neigborhoods and types of buildings.
dct_publisher_sm: Rabat [Morocco] : Société Marocaine de la Photo-Topographie, 1951.
